        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>limited access highways [300008237], highways [300008220], roads by form [300008219], roads [300008217], transportation spaces [300122438], open spaces by function [300129929], open spaces [300008072], Open Spaces and Site Elements (hierarchy name ) [300139081], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
